{"tid":1467631,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[賽後檢討]大前提：香港警察喺機場雖然唔用得tg，但今晚唔會咩都唔做","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:35:19.000Z","uid":229479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7e780d36d2e0e1b58f220392cfe1db2614232eab","tid":1467631,"uid":229479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:12.000Z","msg":"基於呢個前提，到目前為止，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">專登放啲鬼出黎再引大家捉</span></strong>最似佢地作為<br />\n<br />\n目的：<br />\n製造混亂，破壞機場=和理非嘅形象<br />\n分散力量，冇人圍離境或者留喺入境做文宣<br />\n俾位香港官媒tvb/中国官媒大做文章<br />\n警察救人攞番分<br />\n<br />\n發夢喺現場係好易俾鬼影響頭腦，變得<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">憤怒</span></strong>。但大家做每一步都要保持清醒，特別係冇大台嘅時候，好多野要靠自己冷靜判斷。<br />\n<br />\n記住：<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Big Brother is Watching You</span></span></strong><br />\n香港警察一定會暗中玩野<br />\n<br />\n記住：821 721 五大訴求"},{"pid":"c92c33c7ce78ea385acaeeb618060813138f8942","tid":1467631,"uid":304510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:02.000Z","msg":"【文宣組】拆掂今日機場事件的方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467276\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467276</a>"},{"pid":"b852fd9d1712676c310bd196b9c91bd74607ea0d","tid":1467631,"uid":229479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"135b38e053ab140d38da03864cf01ff37f287019","tid":1467631,"uid":229479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bf9bd793403cc9b8607f326ada891ae49743a33","tid":1467631,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5a935b187f3dab789fef2d6799da6027b11c6b","tid":1467631,"uid":55231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:30.000Z","msg":"出左禁制命 機場牌已經玩完"},{"pid":"a62404d5a915e78b12b8dc372bf1e